== Overview ==
The Morning Star is a launch system for mini Magmatic rockets. On impact the explosive cocktail erupts into a splattering of super heated liquid, giving off a fantastic fireworks show as well as melting any targets within range.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Morning Star can be bought in the workshop after obtaining [[Magma Technology]].
